metadata.name: Light and darkness
metadata.description:
【光と闇】どちらが光でどちらが闇か　全ては愛から成り立つ　歪んだ愛も愛である　光と闇は常に交わることはないが共存する　許すことで愛の波動は高く宇宙に繋がる　私は感謝を忘れない
[Light and darkness] Which is light and which is darkness? Everything consists of love. Distorted love is also love. Light and darkness do not always intersect, but coexist. By allowing, the vibration of love is high and leads to the universe. I thank you. will not forget
